      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET DREAMS NZ (6) is a newcomer to the Amanda Turnbull yard from NZ where she was last seen winning at Addington nine weeks ago. Readied with an easy trial win here so can kick off in Australia on the right note. ROCKSIE ROCK (1) has been producing some decent efforts from the back row including a second at Penrith two starts ago. Placed the last time he raced here and gets the ace draw. DUFFY HOLLOW NZ (3) came from wider on this row to win two back at this circuit and distance then drew on the second line and went back last start but worked home in good style to finish a nose from the winner in second. Has the benefit of a good draw. Go well again. LUCKY ZARA (2) is racing well, placing in both starts here since a Dubbo win. Has drawn to advantage so has first four claims.",
